own w-4 h-4 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button><!----></div><div class="relative"><button class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-[#c8e600]"><img src="/assets/PLANKA_enterprisey_glyph_white_duo_inverse_256-C1dEXeKQ.png" alt="" class="w-5 h-5 transition-all duration-300"> Pro <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-400 text-yellow-900 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">New</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-4 h-4 transition-transform lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button><!----></div><a href="/pricing" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-[#c8e600]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-4 h-4 lucide-credit-card-icon lucide-credit-card w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg> Pricing</a><div class="relative"><button class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-1 text-white hover:text-[#c8e600]">Resources <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-4 h-4 transition-transform lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down w-4 h-4 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button><!----></div><button class="ml-2 px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-4 h-4 lucide-play-icon lucide-play w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z"></path></svg> Demo</button></div><div class="flex items-center space-x-4"><div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 border backdrop-blur-sm border-white/30 bg-white/20" role="group" aria-label="Language selection"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide text-white w-4 h-4 lucide-languages-icon lucide-languages text-white w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m5 8 6 6"></path><path d="m4 14 6-6 2-3"></path><path d="M2 5h12"></path><path d="M7 2h1"></path><path d="m22 22-5-10-5 10"></path><path d="M14 18h6"></path></svg><button class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold transition-all duration-200 text-white hover:bg-white/20" aria-label="Deutsch" aria-pressed="false"> DE </button><button class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold transition-all duration-200 bg-[#c8e600] text-gray-900 shadow-md" aria-label="English" aria-pressed="true"> EN </button></div><button class="lg:hidden p-2 rounded-lg transition-colors text-white hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Open navigation menu" aria-expanded="false"><svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path></svg></button></div></div></div><!----></nav><main id="main-content" class="flex-grow"><div><section class="relative flex items-center justify-center text-white overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85), rgba(42, 42, 42, 0.8)), url(&quot;/assets/hero-home-DQWeiHuv.png&quot;) center center / cover no-repeat; min-height: 100vh;"><div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20"><div class="absolute top-20 right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div><div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-[#d9f033] rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div><div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#a0b800] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 0.75s;"></div></div><div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-28 pb-20 text-center"><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-6"><img src="/assets/PLANKA_community_glyph_white_inverse_256-DnoZa8H4.png" alt="PLANKA Community" class="w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 drop-shadow-2xl"><span class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white/80">+</span><img src="/assets/PLANKA_enterprisey_glyph_white_duo_inverse_256-C1dEXeKQ.png" alt="PLANKA Pro" class="w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 drop-shadow-2xl"></div><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6">Project Management. Reimagined. Battle-tested.</h1><p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">The self-hosted Kanban solution that puts you in control. Feature-rich and designed for teams that value privacy and flexibility.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12"><a href="/community" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300">Community Edition</a><a href="/pro" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#c8e600] text-gray-900 font-bold rounded-xl shadow-2xl hover:bg-[#d9f033] transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">Pro Edition <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 ml-2 lucide-arrow-right-icon lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5 ml-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#c8e600]">11100+</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">GitHub Stars</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#c8e600]">8.1M+</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Docker Pulls</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#c8e600]">35+</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Languages</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#c8e600]">100%</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Fair Use License</div></div><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#c8e600]">2019</div><div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Since</div></div></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-8 h-8 text-white/50 lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down w-8 h-8 text-white/50" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></section><section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-[#a0b800] bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">What is PLANKA?</h2><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">PLANKA is a modern Kanban project management tool for teams who like to visualize and successfully organize their tasks. With our Fair Use License, we offer a powerful, self-hosted alternative to proprietary tools.</p><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">From small teams to large organizations - PLANKA grows with your requirements while giving you full control over your data and infrastructure...</p><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">...and it looks damn good.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4"><a href="https://github.com/plankanban/planka" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 mr-2 lucide-github-icon lucide-github w-5 h-5 mr-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"></path><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"></path></svg> GitHub </a><a href="https://docs.planka.cloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 mr-2 lucide-file-text-icon lucide-file-text w-5 h-5 mr-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"></path><path d="M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg> Documentation</a></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#c8e600]/20 to-[#d9f033]/20 rounded-3xl p-8"><div class="relative"><img src="/assets/screenshots/planka-project-overview.png" alt="PLANKA Screenshot" class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl transition-opacity duration-700 opacity-100"><img src="/assets/screenshots/planka-board-overview.png" alt="PLANKA Screenshot" class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl transition-opacity duration-700 opacity-0 absolute inset-0"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gray-50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-[#a0b800] bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Our Story</h2><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">PLANKA was born from the need for a simple, self-hosted project management solution.</p></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-7 h-7 text-gray-900 lucide-lightbulb-icon lucide-lightbulb w-7 h-7 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">The Idea</h3><p class="text-gray-600">We wanted to elegantly manage our projects with a tool that is easy to use, subtly showcases its powerful capabilities, and respects our data.</p></div><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-7 h-7 text-gray-900 lucide-code-icon lucide-code w-7 h-7 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16 18 6-6-6-6"></path><path d="m8 6-6 6 6 6"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Community Driven</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Developed transparently from day one, PLANKA thrives on an amazing community. Every feature is crafted with community input and feedback.</p></div><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"><div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-7 h-7 text-gray-900 lucide-users-icon lucide-users w-7 h-7 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Growing Community</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Today, PLANKA is used by tens of thousands of teams worldwide. Our community continues to grow, contributing ideas, translations, and improvements.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-[#a0b800] bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Our Journey</h2></div><div class="relative"><div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#c8e600] to-[#a0b800]"></div><div class="space-y-12"><div class="relative flex items-center md:flex-row"><div class="w-full md:flex-1 md:pr-8 md:text-right"><div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full md:inline-block md:max-w-md"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8e600] mb-2">2019</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">First Commit</h3><p class="text-gray-600">PLANKA Community project started with the first commit to solve real team collaboration challenges.</p></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-6 h-6 text-gray-900 lucide-code-icon lucide-code w-6 h-6 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m16 18 6-6-6-6"></path><path d="m8 6-6 6 6 6"></path></svg></div><div class="hidden md:block md:flex-1 md:pl-8"></div></div><div class="relative flex items-center md:flex-row-reverse"><div class="w-full md:flex-1 md:pl-8 md:text-left"><div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full md:inline-block md:max-w-md"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8e600] mb-2">2021</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Version 1.0</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Community v1.0 launched with core Kanban features, real-time sync, and Docker support. Community growing steadily.</p></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-6 h-6 text-gray-900 lucide-rocket-icon lucide-rocket w-6 h-6 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"></path><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"></path><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"></path><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"></path></svg></div><div class="hidden md:block md:flex-1 md:pr-8"></div></div><div class="relative flex items-center md:flex-row"><div class="w-full md:flex-1 md:pr-8 md:text-right"><div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full md:inline-block md:max-w-md"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8e600] mb-2">2022</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Pro Development</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Development of PLANKA Pro begins. Community version reaches 2,000 GitHub stars with growing international recognition.</p></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-6 h-6 text-gray-900 lucide-zap-icon lucide-zap w-6 h-6 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><div class="hidden md:block md:flex-1 md:pl-8"></div></div><div class="relative flex items-center md:flex-row-reverse"><div class="w-full md:flex-1 md:pl-8 md:text-left"><div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full md:inline-block md:max-w-md"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8e600] mb-2">2024</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Going Viral</h3><p class="text-gray-600">PLANKA Software GmbH founded and the Community explodes from 3,500 to 8,000 stars - reaching 5,000 in March alone!</p></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-6 h-6 text-gray-900 lucide-trending-up-icon lucide-trending-up w-6 h-6 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 7h6v6"></path><path d="m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17"></path></svg></div><div class="hidden md:block md:flex-1 md:pr-8"></div></div><div class="relative flex items-center md:flex-row"><div class="w-full md:flex-1 md:pr-8 md:text-right"><div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full md:inline-block md:max-w-md"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8e600] mb-2">2025</div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Major Release</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Community v2.0 and Pro Edition released. Now 11,000+ GitHub stars and 35+ languages supported.</p></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full items-center justify-center shadow-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-6 h-6 text-gray-900 lucide-star-icon lucide-star w-6 h-6 text-gray-900" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z"></path></svg></div><div class="hidden md:block md:flex-1 md:pl-8"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5"><div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#c8e600] rounded-full blur-3xl"></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#d9f033] rounded-full blur-3xl"></div></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10"><div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-animate"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-[#c8e600] bg-clip-text text-transparent section-heading mx-auto">What Users Say</h2></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 scroll-animate scroll-animate-delay-100"><p class="text-lg mb-6 italic"> "PLANKA has revolutionized our project management. The simple operation and clear design make it the perfect tool for our team." </p><div class="flex items-center gap-4"><img src="data:image/webp;base64," alt="Project Manager" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"><div><p class="font-semibold">Project Manager</p><p class="text-sm text-[#c8e600]">Software Company</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 scroll-animate scroll-animate-delay-200"><p class="text-lg mb-6 italic"> "Finally a Kanban tool we can host ourselves. Real-time synchronization works flawlessly and setup was a breeze." </p><div class="flex items-center gap-4"><img src="/assets/person2-CMJGR3xO.webp" alt="IT Administrator" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"><div><p class="font-semibold">IT Administrator</p><p class="text-sm text-[#c8e600]">Mid-sized Company</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-lg p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 scroll-animate scroll-animate-delay-300"><p class="text-lg mb-6 italic"> "As developers, we appreciate the transparency and active community behind PLANKA. A great project!" </p><div class="flex items-center gap-4"><img src="/assets/person3-BcKZKi6T.webp" alt="Development Team" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"><div><p class="font-semibold">Development Team</p><p class="text-sm text-[#c8e600]">Software Startup</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gray-50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-16"><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-[#a0b800] bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Choose Your Edition</h2><p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Whether you are a small team or a large enterprise, we have the right solution for you.</p></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-stretch"><div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-[#c8e600] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col"><div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6"><img src="/assets/PLANKA_community_glyph_light_inverse_256-C8NMg6Zq.png" alt="Community" class="w-12 h-12"><div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Community</h3><span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Self-Hosted or Cloud</span></div></div><p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">All core features included. Self-host for free or choose our managed cloud hosting.</p><ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow"><li class="flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 lucide-check-icon lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Unlimited boards &amp; cards</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 lucide-check-icon lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Real-time synchronization</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 lucide-check-icon lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Self-hosted free</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 lucide-check-icon lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Cloud hosting available</span></li></ul><a href="/community" class="block w-full text-center px-6 py-3 bg-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors mt-auto">Learn More <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide w-4 h-4 inline ml-2 lucide-arrow-right-icon lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 inline ml-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div><div class="bg-gradient-to